-- Central Bank's Ma Says Monetary Policy Faces New Challenges, News Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-08T00:21:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/central-bank-s-ma-says-monetary-policy-faces-new-challenges-news-reports.html

          
          
             Deputy Chinese Central Bank Governor
Ma Delun said the People’s Bank of China’s monetary policy faces
many new challenges as its focus moves from money supply to
controlling inflation, the Shanghai Securities News reported.  
 China faces a “huge challenge” on its balance of
international payments because of continuing inflows of money
from abroad, the Shanghai-based newspaper reported.  
